data.description: Gorgeous all brick home in a great location! Stunning entry to open living room with a stone fireplace and raised hearth., multi trey ceiling and hickory hardwood floors. The kitchen is a chef's dream with granite counter tops and a breakfast bar. The open layout seamlessly connects the kitchen to the dining area and living space, making it perfect for hosting gatherings with family and friends. Split bedroom floor plan with a spacious master suite that features a massive walk-in closet and a luxurious bathroom. Water feature pond in the front and a relaxing Koi pond in the backyard with a full outdoor kitchen. Screened porch with the view towards the mountains. The subdivision has captivating waterfall entrance, pavilion, playground and sidewalks. Don't miss the chance to make it your own!
